10:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Bardeen is best suited for sales teams, recruiters, individual professionals, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Kissflow, meanwhile, shines for mid market companies, process owners, HR teams, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2020, Bardeen describes itself as \"AI-powered browser automation that runs in your Chrome tab.\" Kissflow, established in 2012, positions itself as \"Low-code work platform for process automation and project management.\" With 8 years between them, Kissflow brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while Bardeen offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
11:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Bardeen** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (7.0 vs 6.0), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Kissflow is a poor choice — far from it. Kissflow excels in its own right, particularly for mid market companies and process owners.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value runs directly in browser—no server needed, go with Bardeen. If combines workflow and project management matters more to you, Kissflow is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
